    <item>
      <title>油轮和能源公司对红海航线的评价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/what-tanker-and-energy-companies-are-saying-about-red-sea-route</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国航运公司HMM Co.已指示其集装箱船避开苏伊士运河，而台湾的长荣航运公司也暂时停止了以色列的进出口服务，因为也门海岸的胡塞武装袭击开始关闭红海的商船。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/what-tanker-and-energy-companies-are-saying-about-red-sea-route</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 17:31:42 GMT</pubDate>
